"```sql\nSELECT AVG(t.amount) AS average_credit_card_withdrawal\nFROM trans t\nJOIN account a ON t.account_id = a.account_id\nWHERE t.operation = 'VYBER KARTOU'\n  AND YEAR(t.date) = 2021\nGROUP BY MONTH(t.date);\n```\n\nThis SQL query calculates the average amount of credit card withdrawals made by account holders in each month of the year 2021. It uses the `operation` column to filter transactions that are credit card withdrawals (`VYBER KARTOU`) and groups the results by month."